sequenceDiagram
    participant G as Guardian
    participant PCP as PCP (on-device)
    participant Agent as Service Agent
    participant P as Principal (Elder)

    G->>PCP: Declare capabilities (v1)
    Note over PCP: vision: low, language: te,<br/>cognitive: mild_decline,<br/>decision_capacity: fluctuating

    Agent->>PCP: Read PCP
    Agent->>Agent: Compute InteractionModality<br/>(voice, Telugu, slow, max 2 options)

    Agent->>Agent: ConsentCapacityCheck<br/>(passive: 10:15 AM, 1 interaction today)
    Note over Agent: capacity_signal: 0.82<br/>recommendation: proceed

    Agent->>P: Voice call in Telugu<br/>"Amma, two home aide options..."
    P->>Agent: "First one sounds good"
    Agent->>Agent: Create ConsentRecord<br/>with PACE metadata

    Note over Agent: 6 weeks later...
    Agent->>PCP: WelfareTrace check
    Note over PCP: interaction_success_rate: 0.78<br/>ccc_trend: stable
